Network library and associated test programs in C++23.

This project has been tested on the following platforms:

+===========+=====================+==========================+========+========+
| OS Family | Distro/Environment  | OS Version (Port)        | GCC    | Clang  |
+===========+=====================+==========================+========+========+
| GNU/Linux | Fedora              | 42 (x86_64)              | 15.1.1 | 20.1.7 |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------------+--------+--------+
| GNU/Linux | Oracle              | 9.6 (x86_64)             | 14.2.1 | 19.1.7 |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------------+--------+--------+
| GNU/Linux | Oracle              | 10.0 (x86_64)            | 14.2.1 | 19.1.7 |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------------+--------+--------+
| GNU/Linux | openSUSE Tumbleweed | 20250630 (x86_64)        | 15.1.1 | 20.1.7 |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------------+--------+--------+
| GNU/Linux | Ubuntu              | 25.04 (x86_64)           | 14.2.0 | 20.1.2 |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------------+--------+--------+
| Unix      | Apple macOS         | 15.5 (arm64)             | N/A    | 20.1.7 |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------------+--------+--------+
| Windows   | Cygwin              | 10.0 (amd64)             | 16.0.0 | N/A    |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------------+--------+--------+
| Windows   | MinGW               | 10.0 (amd64)             | 15.1.0 | 20.1.7 |
+-----------+---------------------+--------------------------+--------+--------+

